title: NE
content:
[Neurological examination]
E4V5M6, alert
Pupil reflex 3+/3+
EOM full, VF intact, ptosis(-), nystagmus(-)
Facial sensation: onion skin normal, light touch symmetrical
Facial palsy(-)
Tongue deviation(-)
Dysarthria(-)
[Muscle power]
RUL5, RLL5, LUL5, LLL5
DTR: L4 ++/++
Babinski(R/L): withdraw/withdraw
FNF: no dysmetria
HKS: no dysmetria
Light touch: intact
Pinprick: intact
